quagga.input.subject: eThink About It: 02/05/01
quagga.input.body:
Join Cindy Olson, executive vice president of Human Resources and Community 
Affairs, Tuesday, February 6 at 10:00 am Houston time.  Cindy will conduct an 
open-mike discussion about Enron's latest PRC process.  Remember: If you 
can't make the live event, visit the eSpeak site now and post your 
question(s).

ethink.enron.com
